Ferrets were #vaccinated with RBD-ferritin nanoparticles and produced potent neutralizing antibodies against #SARSCoV2 and did not become ill when infected with the #coronavirus.
Thus, RBD-nanoparticle appears to be an effective #vaccine candidate
